{"tid":1929920,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"（北區人入黎！）如果上水啲垃圾水貨舖執曬，你最想開咩舖？","createTime":"2020-03-17T08:34:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-17T12:23:58.000Z","uid":227031,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"da7e6dbeac78b845d81f7662b1870b119746cb21","tid":1929920,"uid":227031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T08:34:24.000Z","msg":"今日睇睇下ig突然見到呢張圖，勁開心咁同班fd討論想上水開咩舖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實真係好諷刺<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，作為一個社區明明應該有唔同類型嘅舖頭，但係上水就變左藥房放題同擺喼博物館<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以小弟想係連登蒐集下大家嘅意見，留言講下自己最想開咩類型嘅舖頭，俾店主知道北區人有咁嘅需要同願望<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n鼓勵開唔同類型嘅舖頭，發展本土經濟圈！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小弟唔識點出po，sorry for 1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KL76ZFY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKL76ZFY.png&h=e82c82bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖片來源自ig：pp_hker"},{"pid":"d470b80be6a89717e4e3559f41e733f9952b7076","tid":1929920,"uid":8308,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T08:35:19.000Z","msg":"誠品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bf8548a2ccf6687789177733dae63121ce23f74","tid":1929920,"uid":173598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T08:37:07.000Z","msg":"百花齊放"},{"pid":"3fbf9469e6d14e9f50afbfaef094e155a2bde71e","tid":1929920,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T08:45:24.000Z","msg":"尋日個po條友話用黎耕種架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/norma